We're at you-know-who's place.

10
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,170
"You-know-who"?

11
00:00:46,170 --> 00:00:49,210
The one who is making you homunculi search for the Philosopher's Stone?

12
00:00:49,210 --> 00:00:50,860
That's not all.

13
00:00:50,860 --> 00:00:55,440
The one who found us, 
brought us together, and nurtured us.

14
00:00:55,440 --> 00:00:58,990
You're being tricked—all you homunculi who want to become human.

15
00:00:59,270 --> 00:01:01,490
Those who are being tricked are fools.

16
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:03,600
What about you?

17
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:05,460
Yeah, I know.

18
00:01:05,460 --> 00:01:08,750
That person just wants the 
Philosopher's Stone to use personally.

19
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:11,150
So what?

20
00:01:11,150 --> 00:01:15,760
As long as I get to see humans suffer, 
that's good enough for me.

21
00:01:19,930 --> 00:01:22,470
Hey, now, your body is precious.

22
00:01:22,470 --> 00:01:24,020
Don't do anything reckless.

23
00:01:25,710 --> 00:01:26,640
Shoot!

24
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:33,130
How many people do you think Scar killed to make you the Philosopher's Stone?

25
00:01:33,990 --> 00:01:36,070
Of the soldiers who 
charged into Liore,

26
00:01:36,070 --> 00:01:38,410
seven thousand of them 
disappeared in an instant.

27
00:01:39,790 --> 00:01:40,910
They're not dead.

28
00:01:40,910 --> 00:01:42,910
They're all right here.

29
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:47,750
Oh yeah, and the guys that died long ago in Ishbal who were in Scar's right arm

30
00:01:47,750 --> 00:01:49,670
are locked away 
inside there as well.

31
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:52,000
Awesome, awesome!

32
00:01:52,260 --> 00:01:56,290
You've got thousands—tens of thousands—of lives there inside you.

33
